<!-- ============================================================
     /foundation — Tab 1 destination. Build the Foundation (L1-L3).
     Four-step guided onboarding for orgs that don't have agents yet.
     Org Chart → OOS → KPIs → SOPs. Each step links to existing
     OTP capability or shows "Coming soon" with progress placeholder.
     ============================================================ -->

